I hereby declare that I have used generative AI-assisted tools (e.g., ChatGPT, Copilot, etc.) in the creation of this thesis as follows:

// Please check and describe in detail:
- [ ] *No Use:* I did not use any generative AI-assisted tools in the preparation of this thesis.
- [ ] *Language and Style Improvement:* I used generative AI-assisted tools for spelling and grammar correction or to optimize the language and style of my own formulations.
- [ ] *Brainstorming, Structuring, or Source Search:* I used generative AI-assisted tools for brainstorming, structuring, or literature search.
- [ ] *Content Creation or Code Generation:* I used generative AI-assisted tools to generate parts of the text, figures, or software source code. The corresponding parts and the nature of their use are transparently documented in the thesis.

I assure that all parts of the work not marked as AI-generated or AI-assisted have been written independently by me.

